==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''howitzer'''
# A cannon that combines certain characteristics of guns and mortars. The howitzer delivers [[projectile]]s with medium velocities, either by low or high [[trajectories]]. JP 1-02.
# Normally a [[cannon]] with a tube length of 20 to 30 [[caliber]]s; however, the tube length can exceed 30 calibers and still be considered a howitzer when the high angle fire zoning solution permits range overlap between charges. JP 1-02. See also [[gun]]; [[mortar]].

